          <h2>Commands</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong><code>potion-kit chat</code></strong> — Interactive chat.</li>
            <li><strong><code>potion-kit chat "message"</code></strong> — Send one message and exit (one-shot).</li>
            <li><strong><code>potion-kit clear</code></strong> — Clear chat history for this project (next chat starts a new conversation).</li>
            <li><strong><code>potion-kit</code></strong> or <strong><code>potion-kit --help</code></strong> — Show usage and available commands. Unknown commands also show help and do not call the API.</li>
          </ul>
